OL,3,COne person in hospital following
OL,4,Cincident involving a crane at the Port
OL,5,Cof Tyne
OL,7,FOne person has been taken to hospital
OL,8,Ffollowing an incident involving a
OL,9,Fcrane on the River Tyne this afternoon
OL,10,F(Sunday 19 July).
OL,12,FPhotographs appear to show a crane at
OL,13,Fthe Port of Tyne, South Shields, on a
OL,14,Ftanker vessel on the river.
OL,16,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,17,Fshortly after 1pm this afternoon,
OL,18,Fafter it was reported to police that a
OL,19,Fship had collided with a crane.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
