PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784558905
OL,3,COne person in hospital following
OL,4,Cincident involving a crane at the Port
OL,5,Cof Tyne
OL,7,FA man sustained injuries that are not
OL,8,Fbelieved to be life-threatening.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the North East
OL,11,FAmbulance Service said one person was
OL,12,Ftaken to Newcastle's RVI hospital
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident on the dockside.
OL,15,FThe Great North Air Ambulance (GNAS)
OL,16,Fand Tyne and Wear Fire and Rescue were
OL,17,Falso called to the scene.
OL,19,FThe Port of Tyne has been contacted
OL,20,Ffor comment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
