OL,3,COne person in hospital following
OL,4,Cincident involving a crane at the Port
OL,5,Cof Tyne
OL,7,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Just after 1pm today (Sunday),
OL,9,Fwe received a report of concern for
OL,10,Fthe safety of a person at the Port of
OL,11,FTyne in South Shields.
OL,13,F"It was reported that, for reasons yet
OL,14,Fto be established, a ship had collided
OL,15,Fwith a crane.
OL,17,F"Emergency services attended and a man
OL,18,Fwas found to have sustained injuries
OL,19,Fnot believed to be life-threatening.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
