PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784558905
OL,3,COne person in hospital following
OL,4,Cincident involving a crane at the Port
OL,5,Cof Tyne
OL,7,F"He was taken to hospital for
OL,8,Ftreatment, where he remains. Enquiries
OL,9,Fremain ongoing to fully understand the
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, GNAS told ITV Tyne Tees:
OL,13,F"Our critical care team was activated
OL,14,Fat 1.10pm to an incident in South
OL,15,FShields. We had a paramedic and doctor
OL,16,Fon board our aircraft and they arrived
OL,17,Fon scene at 1.23pm.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]
